<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4668166>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 9. Comparison of measurements (means and ranges, in millimetres) for zooarchaeological Zygodontomys specimens from the Grenada Bank, and for extant Zygodontomys populations from mainland Central America and northern South America and Central and South American continental shelf islands, including all currently recognized species and subspecies. A, occlusal length of maxillary molar toothrow; B, breadth of M1 across the protocone-paracone cusp pair. Data for non-Grenada Bank Zygodontomys populations from Voss (1991)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4668166/files/figure.png" .

